[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Over hills and valleys, across rivers and creeks, toward the east.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "He wasted much breath laughing at his smartness as he ran, and soon he grew tired.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "\"'Ho!' he said to himself, 'I am far enough now and I shall sleep. It's easy to steal from the Sun-just as easy as stealing from the Bear or the Beaver.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "\"He folded the leggings and put them under his head as the Sun had done, and went to sleep.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "He had a dream and it waked him with a start. Bad deeds bring bad dreams to us all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "OLD man sat up and there was the Sun looking right in his face and laughing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "He was frightened and ran away, leaving the leggings behind him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "\"Laughingly the Sun put on the leggings and went on toward the west, for he is always busy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "He thought he would see OLD man no more, but it takes more than one lesson to teach a fool to be wise, and OLD man hid in the timber until the Sun had travelled out of sight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "\"He was much afraid this time, but as soon as the Sun was asleep he crept to the lodge and peeked inside.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Here he stopped and looked about, for he was afraid the Sun would hear his heart beating.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "\"All about the lodge were beautiful linings, tanned and painted by the Moon, and the queer signs on them made the old coward tremble.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106729_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106729/7713_106729_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "He heard a night bird call outside and he thought it would surely wake the Sun; so he hastened to the bed and with cunning fingers stole the leggings, as he had done the night before, without waking the great sleeper.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106733_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106733/7713_106733_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Carefully, lest he wake the sleeper, OLD man crept close, being particular not to move a stone or break a twig; for the Mountain lion is much faster than men are, you see; and if OLD man had wakened the Lion, he would never have caught him again, perhaps.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106733_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106733/7713_106733_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Little by little he crept to the stone where the Mountain lion was dreaming, and at last grabbed him by the tail.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106733_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106733/7713_106733_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "It wasn't much of a tail then, but enough for OLD man to hold to.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "OLD MAN AND THE FOX",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "I am sure that the plains Indian never made nor used the stone arrow head.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "I have heard white men say that they had seen Indians use them; but I have never found an Indian that ever used them himself, or knew of their having been used by his people.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Thirty years ago I knew Indians, intimately, who were nearly a hundred years old, who told me that the stone arrow head had never been in use in their day, nor had their fathers used them in their own time.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Indians find these arrow points just as they find the stone mauls and hammers, which I have seen them use thousands of times, but they do not make them any more than they make the stone mauls and hammers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "In the old days, both the head of the lance and the point of the arrow were of bone; even knives were of bone, but some other people surely made the arrow points that are scattered throughout the United States and Europe, I am told.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "One night I asked War Eagle if he had ever known the use, by Indians, of the stone arrow head, and he said he had not.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "He told me that just across the Canadian line there was a small lake, surrounded by trees, wherein there was an island covered with long reeds and grass.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "All about the edge of this island were willows that grew nearly to the water, but intervening there was a narrow beach of stones.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Here, he said, the stone arrow heads had been made by little ghost people who lived there, and he assured me that he had often seen these strange little beings when he was a small boy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Whenever his people were camped by this lake the old folks waked the children at daybreak to see the inhabitants of this strange island; and always when a noise was made, or the sun came up, the little people hid away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000004_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000004_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Often he had seen their heads above the grass and tiny willows, and his grandfather had told him that all the stone arrow heads had been made on that island, and in war had been shot all over the world, by magic bows.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "\"No,\" he said, \"I shall not lie to you, my friend.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "I never saw those little people shoot an arrow, but there are so many arrows there, and so many pieces of broken ones, that it proves that my grandfather was right in what he told me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Besides, nobody could ever sleep on that island.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "I have heard a legend wherein OLD man, in the beginning, killed an animal for the people to eat, and then instructed them to use the ribs of the dead brute to make knives and arrow points.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "I have seen lance heads, made from shank bones, that were so highly polished that they resembled pearl, and I have in my possession bone arrow points such as were used long ago.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "Indians do not readily forget their tribal history, and I have photographed a war bonnet, made of twisted buffalo hair, that was manufactured before the present owner's people had, or ever saw, the horse.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "The owner of this bonnet has told me that the stone arrow head was never used by Indians, and that he knew that ghost people made and used them when the world was young.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7713_106738_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7713/106738/7713_106738_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7713",
        "content": "I have seen hickory bows among the plains Indians, too, and these were longer and always straight, instead of being fashioned like Cupid's weapon.",
